  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion of patients with chronic severe entheropathy and of their healthy relatives
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Main Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe chronic enteropathy

          -  Patients developing their first symptoms within the first 6 years of life and, in
             priority within the first two years of life, or patients with a disease of later
             onset, in case of a familial history suggestive of inherited mutations notably in
             families comprising several affected members

          -  OR : Be a patient's relative, even if presenting with enteropathy of later onset.

        Main Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject having participated to any therapeutical clinical study in the 30 days
             preceding the inclusion in this study,
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
